"BOH, Stock Associate, adidas Retail Store, SP Toronto (#2060) - Toronto, ON - Indeed.com","Purpose:
An Adidas stock associate is responsible for receiving, organizing, and maintaining store inventory. The job description of a stock associate requires a close attention to detail, the ability to conduct moderate to heavy physical labor, and strong organizational skills.
Key Responsibilities:
Assists in all BOH (Back of House) duties i.e., receiving/processing of shipment, stock placement
Auditing stock levels to ensure inventory accuracy
Using internal programs i.e., Brim, Stock Hero to locate merchandise for bring to sales floor for customer
Knowledge of SFS (Ship from Store)
Assisting in monthly transfers provided from Allocation team
Hanging and prepping of merchandise for Sales Floor
Maintenance of cleanliness of stock room i.e., cleaning supplies, SFS supplies, garbages etc.
Responsible for assisting with the preparation of yearly inventory counts
Communicates the product levels and assortments with management.
Adheres to adidas’ brand values and Sales Associate competencies.
Assist with telephone duties.
Adheres to company policy and procedures relating to inventory control.
Other duties as required by store management.
